Uttar Pradesh
Dec 11, 2014
Sexual Harassment at Work, Other
Description:
			A teacher of a school was arrested today for allegdly showing blue film to children in Ambedkar colony falling under Krishna Nagar police station limits here.

Jitendra Gautam started showing blue film to the children on his mobile phone when the principal of Takshasila Public School had gone out for an urgent work.

Residents of the area badly assaulted him and handed him over to police.

On receiving information about the incident, the principal of the school rushed back and filed a complaint.

"He has been arrested and a case has been registered against him on the complaint of Urmila Sharma, the principal of the school," DySP Anil Yadav said.


